{"tid":1127952,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"祖雲達斯想回購普巴 曼聯開價1.3億","createTime":"2019-04-27T12:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T13:21:03.000Z","uid":186071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e49d22e1d9305bd329c7301a12c728bd5df97d45","tid":1127952,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T12:53:05.000Z","msg":"【#轉會SportsLight】<br />\n<br />\n《衛報》記者、Di Marzio團隊成員Fabrizio Romano報導，#祖雲達斯 欲回購中場普巴，預料 #曼聯 還價1.3億歐元（1.12億鎊）。報道指，祖雲達斯已與普巴經理人拉奧拿（Mino Raiola）接洽。由於C朗拿度的高薪，祖雲達斯如欲得到普巴，或要出售比真歷、杜格拉斯哥斯達等球員騰出薪酬空間。普巴在2012年離開曼聯，此後四年效力祖雲達斯，直至2016年夏季回歸曼聯。<br />\n<br />\n除了祖雲達斯，#皇家馬德里 表明想得到普巴，但尚未開出正式報價。<br />\n<br />\n#體嘢"},{"pid":"353ea3c6f5329b044d339642cddc9b6581935901","tid":1127952,"uid":214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T13:03:38.000Z","msg":"痴𨶙線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1.3億"},{"pid":"99c77dded30b39c971eda500feb4ab0f90c0fd44","tid":1127952,"uid":198866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T13:04:41.000Z","msg":"哩兩隊互相將同一件野買黎買去係咪洗黑錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d1075727bfdc0473900a0ead3b2438fbcb44ad","tid":1127952,"uid":247518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"係意甲散步 應該無咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0af45599a574112e431b694ee6917695a8ba31","tid":1127952,"uid":96877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T13:05:52.000Z","msg":"牙朗交換普巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54441bca9138888c63d38e93ccd83a2346f395a","tid":1127952,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T13:06:10.000Z","msg":"#Pogback"},{"pid":"71c5296c3e8cf425d5d24a4bfdf01e04eabc3e45","tid":1127952,"uid":41434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d0af45599a574112e431b694ee6917695a8ba31","tid":1127952,"uid":